@{
    if (ViewBag.Nivel == "Cliente")
    {
        Layout = "_LayoutCliente";
    }
    if (ViewBag.Nivel == "Admin")
    {
        Layout = "_LayoutAdmin";
    }
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Intuitive:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Insane Mechanical</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/site.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: grey;
            background-image: url(https://st2.depositphotos.com/1175677/12327/v/450/depositphotos_123277816-stock-illustration-black-wood-background-wallpaper-backdrop.jpg);
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 60px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin-top: 80px;
            font-weight: 600;
            animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out;
        }

        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .content-all {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .section-content {
            flex: 2;
            padding: 0 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .section-image {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .section-image img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 10px;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

                .section-image img:hover {
                    transform: scale(1.1);
                }

        .media-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

            .media-section img,
            .media-section video {
                margin: 10px;
                max-width: 100%;
                border: 2px solid white;
                border-radius: 10px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

                .media-section img:hover,
                .media-section video:hover {
                    transform: scale(1.1);
                }

            .media-section video {
                max-height: 300px;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

        .welcome-text {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .carousel {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
        }

            .carousel img {
                max-height: 300px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Insane Mechanical</h1>
    <div class="content-all">
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-content">
                <h2>¿Cómo funcionan los motores de los automóviles?</h2>
                <p>“El motor de combustión interna consta de cilindros, pistones, inyectores de combustible y bujías. Combinados, estos componentes queman combustible y dejan salir los gases de escape de los cilindros. Al repetir el proceso, crea energía que impulsa el automóvil.”</p>
            </div>
            <div class="section-image">
                <img src="~/Motor.png" alt="Motor de automóvil">
            </div>
        </div>
        <img src="~/Carrofordummies.jpg" class="d-block mx-auto" />
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
